https://blog.csdn.net/yessharing/article/details/55806090#1apt%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F

1. apt使用代理

    a. 修改/etc/apt/apt.conf（或者/etc/envrionment
    b. 增加
        Acquire::http::proxy "http://127.0.0.1:8000/";
        Acquire::ftp::proxy "ftp://127.0.0.1:8000/";
        Acquire::https::proxy "https://127.0.0.1:8000/";

2. apt更换源

    a. 备份 sudo cp /etc/apt/sources.list /etc/apt/sources.list.bak
    b. 编辑 sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list
    c. 写入国内源

